The old mine
According to tradition an orc becomes a warrior only when he receives an axe from the hands of a chief. The Praetor should gather the material for the axe in the mines of the Dead City.
#subobj 1
Find the entrance to the mine
The location of the mine is south-east of the orc fortress.
#subobj 2
Go to the old mine
The old mine is located just to the east of the mine. Don't forget that abandoned mines are home to undead.
#subobj 3
Get to the north tunnel.
Only in the north tunnel can you get the right material for weapons.
#subobj 4
Get the materials
The miners in the ore mine have worked well in this area. The material is already mined, you just need to carry it out.